#: ../../quickstart.rst:2 e7c0c77d3ae24f3cb632645d5b8c3913
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "快速开始"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:4 064ed5be324b4624877a60749a44c846
msgid ""
"This page gets you from zero to a working VoxCPM setup as fast as "
"possible. Follow it top to bottom and you will have generated audio "
"through three different paths: the Python API, the CLI, and the web demo."
msgstr ""
"本页会尽可能快速地带你从零完成可运行的 VoxCPM 安装。按顺序往下操作后，你就可以通过三种方式生成语音：Python API、CLI "
"和网页演示。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:7 93bb3efc4cbc45ed90ba79efca313c4a
msgid "Install"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:13 1f6f02c8a99d44888464471c02d3e3f1
msgid ""
"That's it. For other installation methods (pip, source checkout, etc.), "
"see :doc:`./installation`."
msgstr "到这里就完成了。若你想了解其他安装方式（如 pip、从源码安装等），请参阅 :doc:`./installation`。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:16 3f6bdcde15e4452c9d04e04c29c1c8ee
msgid "Step 1: Python API"
msgstr "第 1 步：使用 Python API"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:18 78d7f8df7ab24ed382314b9ab0eb5944
msgid "Start with the current recommended release, ``VoxCPM 2``:"
msgstr "从当前推荐版本 ``VoxCPM 2`` 开始："

#: ../../quickstart.rst:38 809bac7341c444bf81f88e9441da313f
msgid ""
"The first run downloads model weights automatically. If you have trouble "
"accessing Hugging Face, see the mirror setup in :doc:`./installation`."
msgstr "首次运行会自动下载模型权重。如果你访问 Hugging Face 有困难，请查看 :doc:`./installation` 中的镜像配置。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:40 2215621deaf04eb6a694b89133c72088
msgid ""
"This example does not enable the optional denoiser — it is only needed "
"when you want to enhance prompt or reference audio for voice cloning. See"
" :doc:`./usage_guide` for details."
msgstr ""
"这个示例没有启用可选降噪器。只有当你想在声音克隆时增强 prompt 或 reference 音频时才需要它。详情见 "
":doc:`./usage_guide`。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:42 0a70f48b77954a49a6b7dc7d57a29967
msgid ""
"If this script runs and produces ``demo.wav``, your installation is "
"working."
msgstr "如果这段脚本可以正常运行并生成 ``demo.wav``，说明你的安装已可正常工作。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:46 33a6082d45b44732885bf1ea9b569c3c
msgid ""
"Runtime device selection is automatic by default. "
"``VoxCPM.from_pretrained(..., device=\"auto\")`` prefers ``cuda -> mps ->"
" cpu``. You can also force a device explicitly with ``device=\"cpu\"``, "
"``device=\"mps\"``, ``device=\"cuda\"``, or ``device=\"cuda:0\"``. If you"
" hit platform-specific ``torch.compile`` issues, try ``optimize=False``."
msgstr ""
"运行时设备选择默认是自动的。"
"``VoxCPM.from_pretrained(..., device=\"auto\")`` 会按 ``cuda -> mps -> cpu`` "
"的顺序优先选择设备。你也可以显式指定 ``device=\"cpu\"``、``device=\"mps\"``、``device=\"cuda\"`` "
"或 ``device=\"cuda:0\"``。如果你遇到平台相关的 ``torch.compile`` 问题，可以尝试 ``optimize=False``。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:53 903df20e24064e7e89d899aaad56b660
msgid ""
"For new projects, start with :doc:`./models/voxcpm2`, which is the "
"current version. Earlier releases remain available from "
":doc:`./models/version_history` when you need an older checkpoint."
msgstr ""
"对于新项目，建议从当前版本 :doc:`./models/voxcpm2` 开始。如果你需要较旧的 checkpoint，也可以在 "
":doc:`./models/version_history` 中找到早期版本。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:56 78795fe4e731457a941fe0bbcb67afac
msgid "Step 2: CLI"
msgstr "第 2 步：使用命令行"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:58 7a4d84efca2f4034a507a6d9bc577448
msgid ""
"VoxCPM also provides a command-line interface. The CLI defaults to "
"``openbmb/VoxCPM2``, so you can use the recommended subcommands directly "
"unless you want to override the checkpoint with ``--hf-model-id``:"
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM 也提供命令行接口。CLI 默认使用 ``openbmb/VoxCPM2``，因此除非你想通过 ``--hf-model-id`` "
"覆盖 checkpoint，否则可以直接使用推荐子命令："

#: ../../quickstart.rst:82 73f645af7ff54b118490160a5c2bb628
msgid "Step 3: Web Demo"
msgstr "第 3 步：使用网页演示"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:84 8ff1b86ae6a1417da1b094adbf378cc2
msgid ""
"The web demo requires a source checkout. If you installed via ``pip "
"install voxcpm`` in the step above, you still need to clone the "
"repository:"
msgstr "网页演示需要克隆源码仓库。如果你在上一步通过 ``pip install voxcpm`` 完成安装，仍然需要克隆仓库："

#: ../../quickstart.rst:93 e3c2b4ebf6144ac894420a4efc81c2f5
msgid ""
"The web demo also downloads an additional ASR model (SenseVoice-Small) on"
" first use for prompt audio transcription."
msgstr "Web Demo 在首次使用时还会额外下载一个 ASR 模型（SenseVoice-Small），用于 prompt 音频转写。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:96 f0f0bdc2d7ee4723a45bee4a66d7e15b
msgid "What's Next?"
msgstr "接下来做什么？"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:98 c044a47820db4876bca402e2a7aea3a8
msgid ""
"Continue with :doc:`./usage_guide` for prompt strategy, voice cloning "
"tips, and quality tuning."
msgstr "继续阅读 :doc:`./usage_guide`，了解 prompt 策略、声音克隆技巧和质量调优。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:99 1d629bc2803a4cdab5e514480f1b8749
msgid ""
"Check the pages under ``Models`` in the sidebar for version-specific "
"features and migration notes."
msgstr "查看侧边栏 ``Models`` 下的页面，了解各版本特性与迁移说明。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:100 216b434091a44d10a8099f390a36e7c6
msgid ""
"Fine-tune the model with :doc:`./finetuning/finetune` to adapt it to your"
" use case."
msgstr "通过 :doc:`./finetuning/finetune` 微调模型，使其适配你的实际场景。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:101 c1ff174232f6426cb503944b67dcffce
msgid ""
"Deploy the model with :doc:`./deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm` for high-"
"throughput serving."
msgstr "通过 :doc:`./deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm` 部署模型，以实现高吞吐服务。"

